# App routing

- Store admin: **one** layout at `storeAdmin/(dashboard)/[storeId]/layout.tsx` (`StoreAdminLayout`, staff access).
- **`(routes)/` must not have `layout.tsx`** — nested layout caused 404s on deep paths (e.g. notifications/history) under Turbopack dev.
- New pages: `.../[storeId]/(routes)/<feature>/page.tsx` without extra layouts under `(routes)`.
